title: Military Raaj
subTitle: Major Anand is reassigned to a camp for unruly cadets but soon finds himself confronting deeper threats as lawlessness rises and the authorities struggle to maintain order.

subTitle: Children venture out on a pilgrimage and visit several holy shrines devoted to different gods, so that they can please them and ask for their help.

title: Fox
subTitle: Arjun, an accomplished but corrupt criminal lawyer who has the habit of winning each case he fights, decides to turn over a new leaf. However, soon he is accused of killing five people.

title: Krazzy 4
subTitle: A psychiatrist takes four patients, with an intellectual disability, to watch a cricket match but gets kidnapped. The group tries to find her and seek the help of a girl working for a television channel.

subTitle: After DSP Vishal arrests two thugs, their boss kidnaps the commissioner's daughter. But after Vishal rescues the girl and jails the thugs, they return to hurt Vishal and the commissioner's families.

title: Chatrapathi

title: Haan Maine Bhi Pyaar Kiya
subTitle: Pooja divorces her husband for being unfaithful and gets a job as secretary to a film star. The two fall in love, before her ex-husband returns and she finds herself confused between the two men.

title: Badal
subTitle: Badal's family dies at the hands of a corrupt police officer. While he is raised by his father's friend, he turns into a terrorist and vows to avenge his family's death.

title: Gopi Kishan
subTitle: Policeman Gopi's doppelganger Kishan, who is a criminal, learns about the former and uses his identity to his advantage as he tries to find his father. This results in Gopi reaping the benefits.

title: Gunda Gardi

title: Chor Machaaye Shor
